1.title: Episode #1.1
1.plot: Four young women of faith try to navigate their morality and individuality through the adventures of living and dating in Atlanta. In this episode Isla tells the girls about her eventful night with her boyfriend King which does not end well because she has decided to be celibate.

2.title: Episode #1.2
2.plot: Four young women of faith try to navigate their morality and individuality through the adventures of living and dating in Atlanta. In this episode Tina confronts her boyfriend Ryan about his life goals and their living situation.

3.title: Episode #1.3
3.plot: Four young women of faith try to navigate their morality and individuality through the adventures of living and dating in Atlanta. Ester planned a romantic evening for her husband but he is consumed with other spiritual commitments.

4.title: Episode #1.4
4.plot: Four young women of faith try to navigate their morality and individuality through the adventures of living and dating in Atlanta. Renee goes on a bind date with Justin. The date is going well until she reveals an unexpected truth that may be a deal breaker.

5.title: Episode #1.5
5.plot: Follow four young women of faith as they navigate living and dating in Atlanta!!

imdb.plot outline: Follow Isla, Tina, Ester and Renee on a Sunday brunch as they recap the past 24 hours of their lives. Season one finds Isla on the brink of becoming celibate, which drastically affects her relationship with her boyfriend, King. Tina deals with an unemployed boyfriend that has overstayed his welcome. Ester works to maintain the facade of being in a happy marriage; and Renee finally meets someone she's genuinely interested in, only for him to share that he wants to have children. Follow these women as they mold, create, and re-define their moral compass.
